-------------------------------------------------------------------
18) DB INDEX VE BUTUNLUK KURALLARI (ZORUNLU)
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Gecis kontrolunun hizli calismasi icin:

Zorunlu indexler:
- vehicles(country_code, plate_text)
- vehicle_subscriptions(vehicle_id, status, end_date)
- access_events(event_time)

Zorunlu butunluk kurallari:
- users.email unique
- vehicles (country_code + plate_text) unique
- payment SUCCESS olmadan ACTIVE abonelik olusmaz

Transactional kural:
- fake odeme SUCCESS ve ACTIVE abonelik yazimi tek transaction icinde yapilir.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
19) API SLA HEDEFI (MVP)
-------------------------------------------------------------------
/api/access/check-plate endpointi icin:
- hedef ortalama yanit suresi: <= 300 ms (DB sorgu kismi)
- p95 hedef: <= 600 ms

Not:
- OCR suresi bu SLA disinda ayrica olculecektir.
